Josephine Hill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Josephine_Hill 0 Josephine Hill (October 3, 1899 – December 17, 1989) was an American actress of the silent era. She appeared in 107 films between 1917 and 1933. She was married to Western star Jack Perrin from 1920 until their divorce in 1937. She was born in San Francisco and died in Palm Springs, California. She is buried at Desert Memorial Park in Cathedral City, California as Josephine Hill Brown. Josephine_Hill ( October_3_,_1899 – December_17_,_1989 ) was an_American_actress of the_silent_era .
